nodes.text: Whyren's Reserve, also spelled Whyrren's Reserve or Rywen's Reserve, was a rare, expensive Corellian whiskey. It had an amber color and a crisp, woody taste. It was a favorite of the black market trade. Wedge Antilles was fond of the drink. Han Solo estimated that a case of extremely rare Whyren's Reserve batch number NN182 was equivalent to, if not more valuable than, the cost of the Millennium Falcon.
